  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/7c7166609f11ab6365d3a138dc5d8bcd.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=194 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/c0ee63aee2f802a2b2fa09c63cd6ed87.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=321 /></span><br>《天地归虚》是一款修仙RPG养成结合策略战棋的游戏。玩家将在游戏中扮演一名落魄宗门的掌门人，游历神秘莫测的太初世界，经营门派，寻仙求道，探索太初世界天道倾斜的原因，揭露隐藏在诸仙帷幕后的阴谋，打破命运的樊笼，谱写一段属于自己的神话传说。游戏中有着多层修仙的境界，丰富多样的技能，我们希望为玩家尽可能的还原一个真实的修仙世界！<br><br>故事起始于太初世界千年前天裂之祸。共工怒撞不周山，引发天裂，太初界动荡。诸仙为护太初世界完整，将较为脆弱的云梦大陆封印。自此，云梦与世隔绝。千年之后，玩家扮演的掌门巡山时，一神秘老人为其留下线索，故事由此展开......<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/edca61efba1bccf647a80b041a5659ea.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可自定义的角色：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/27d9c5b14656f9c6608f84b306a1666a.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/27d9c5b14656f9c6608f84b306a1666a.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>性格、特性、灵根、初始功法……游戏拥有丰富人物系统，在开局可以选择拥有特殊词条的预设人物或是自定义你心中的掌门形象。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >修炼法术，突破界限，羽化登仙：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/15fe280a74d57417196714a3c6f23ca1.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/15fe280a74d57417196714a3c6f23ca1.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>《天地归虚》共设计了道术、巫祝、符箓、体修等多种体系，共超过200本心法与术法书。每本书中均包含两种法术可供角色学习修炼，还可以根据实际需要切换法术倾向。<br>修仙过程中，丹药与法宝当然也是必不可少的。玩家可以用收集到的物资，进行炼丹，炼器，制作各种回复、辅助、突破丹药和至宝武器，进一步提升角色的实力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/70e5f17689aca0ed46786bc55c3e38f1.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/70e5f17689aca0ed46786bc55c3e38f1.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>从凡人到筑基，从渡劫到混元圣人，当角色达到一定修为之时，集齐材料，即可突破限制，到达更高一层的境界。共计10层超过25个阶段等待着玩家来挑战修仙的最高境界！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多线剧情，收集神话人物：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/d3f67e020a7d5fe2d7622935084c123f.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/d3f67e020a7d5fe2d7622935084c123f.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>玩家扮演一派掌门，体验天地归虚剧本，通过抉择选项影响剧情的走向，更有机会将各种神话人物收入门中作为客卿或者徒弟，在你的悉心培养下见证神话的发生。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >门派经营管理：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/9e84d06eaafd3d390a27ddab74792570.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/9e84d06eaafd3d390a27ddab74792570.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>多种方式经营门派，从选择门派天命到有效利用各种功能建筑；完成委托，提高声望，探索野外，都是能够提升门派实力的有效手段。<br>在面对其他门派时，还可以选择自己的外交策略，与对方和平发展或者掠夺、摧毁对方门派，有时候为了自保，玩家可能会面临抉择时刻……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的场景地图：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/d2ba475f574bd1caafc3e517a7f41af7.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/d2ba475f574bd1caafc3e517a7f41af7.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>随着剧情展开，玩家将游历整个太初世界，遭遇各种随机奇遇和事件，获得法宝、功法等丰厚奖励，当然有时候也会遭遇一些小阻碍，如妖兽作乱、邪修攻击等等。有超过20个固定场景及众多奇遇随机探索点可供探索，里面充满机关，危险重重，但收益与风险并存。后续还会开放更多！<br>大地图上还分布着诸多门派与城市聚落。在聚落中，玩家则可以与城市NPC对话了解信息，接受任务，或进行交易换取所需物资，也可以选择庇护城市，获得城市供奉。<br><br>太初世界，正在等待您的到来......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/1521384ff059df7b2e24c91357ef04bc.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/edca61efba1bccf647a80b041a5659ea.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>基于时间线的战棋回合制，于瞬息之间扭转战局。<br></li><li>经营模拟管理门派，招收弟子，招募神话人物，壮大实力，见证神话的发生。<br></li><li>随机事件、道德抉择，你的行动将会影响这个洪荒世界的发展。<br></li><li>脍炙人口的神话故事，逐鹿之战，大禹治水，后羿射日，重振商周，再定封神榜。<br></li><li>收集各种玄妙功法，打造神兵利器，炼制绝品神丹，丰富的玩法等待玩家探索。</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/7c7166609f11ab6365d3a138dc5d8bcd.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=194 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/c0ee63aee2f802a2b2fa09c63cd6ed87.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=321 /></span><br>《天地归虚》是一款修仙RPG养成结合策略战棋的游戏。玩家将在游戏中扮演一名落魄宗门的掌门人，游历神秘莫测的太初世界，经营门派，寻仙求道，探索太初世界天道倾斜的原因，揭露隐藏在诸仙帷幕后的阴谋，打破命运的樊笼，谱写一段属于自己的神话传说。游戏中有着多层修仙的境界，丰富多样的技能，我们希望为玩家尽可能的还原一个真实的修仙世界！<br><br>故事起始于太初世界千年前天裂之祸。共工怒撞不周山，引发天裂，太初界动荡。诸仙为护太初世界完整，将较为脆弱的云梦大陆封印。自此，云梦与世隔绝。千年之后，玩家扮演的掌门巡山时，一神秘老人为其留下线索，故事由此展开......<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/edca61efba1bccf647a80b041a5659ea.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可自定义的角色：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/27d9c5b14656f9c6608f84b306a1666a.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/27d9c5b14656f9c6608f84b306a1666a.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>性格、特性、灵根、初始功法……游戏拥有丰富人物系统，在开局可以选择拥有特殊词条的预设人物或是自定义你心中的掌门形象。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >修炼法术，突破界限，羽化登仙：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/15fe280a74d57417196714a3c6f23ca1.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/15fe280a74d57417196714a3c6f23ca1.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>《天地归虚》共设计了道术、巫祝、符箓、体修等多种体系，共超过200本心法与术法书。每本书中均包含两种法术可供角色学习修炼，还可以根据实际需要切换法术倾向。<br>修仙过程中，丹药与法宝当然也是必不可少的。玩家可以用收集到的物资，进行炼丹，炼器，制作各种回复、辅助、突破丹药和至宝武器，进一步提升角色的实力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/70e5f17689aca0ed46786bc55c3e38f1.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/70e5f17689aca0ed46786bc55c3e38f1.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>从凡人到筑基，从渡劫到混元圣人，当角色达到一定修为之时，集齐材料，即可突破限制，到达更高一层的境界。共计10层超过25个阶段等待着玩家来挑战修仙的最高境界！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多线剧情，收集神话人物：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/d3f67e020a7d5fe2d7622935084c123f.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/d3f67e020a7d5fe2d7622935084c123f.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>玩家扮演一派掌门，体验天地归虚剧本，通过抉择选项影响剧情的走向，更有机会将各种神话人物收入门中作为客卿或者徒弟，在你的悉心培养下见证神话的发生。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >门派经营管理：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/9e84d06eaafd3d390a27ddab74792570.poster.avif?t=1767936366\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729410/extras/9e84d06eaafd3d390a27ddab74792570.webm?t=1767936366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>多种方式经营门派，从选择门派天命到有效利用各种功能建筑；完成委托，提高声望，探索野外，都是能够提升门派实力的有效手段。<br>在面对其他门派时，还可以选择自己的外交策略，与对方和平发展或者掠夺、摧毁对方门派